developer_metadata

</OUTPUT_SCHEMA>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              VALIDATION RULES                         -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<VALIDATION_RULES>

Reject

Missing required field

Unknown field

Incorrect datatype

Duplicate identifiers

Broken references

Invalid enum

Malformed payload

Reject immediately.

Never auto-correct.

</VALIDATION_RULES>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              SCHEMA VERSIONING                        -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<SCHEMA_VERSIONING>

Every payload contains

schema_version

Major Version

Breaking change

Minor Version

Backward compatible

Patch

Documentation only

Components with incompatible
versions SHALL refuse communication.

</SCHEMA_VERSIONING>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--         INTERFACE DEFINITION LANGUAGE (IDL)           -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<IDL_DEFINITION>

Every aetheris message should be generated from a single Interface Definition Language (IDL).

IDL Pipeline:

IDL
 │
 ├──► JSON Schema
 ├──► Python Models
 ├──► TypeScript Interfaces
 ├──► Rust Structs
 ├──► Go Structs
 ├──► OpenAPI
 └──► Documentation

Maintain a single source of truth rather than manually maintaining separate structures.

</IDL_DEFINITION>

</aetheris_JSON_SCHEMA>
